[0.000, "o", "\u001b8\u001b[0m\u001b[49m\u001b[39m\u001b[27m\u001b[24m\u001b[J"]
[0.001, "o", "\r\n[\u001b[33mWARNING\u001b[39m]: Console output during zsh initialization detected.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nWhen using Powerlevel10k with instant prompt, console output during zsh\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "initialization may indicate issues.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nYou can:\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  - \u001b[1mRecommended\u001b[0m: Change \u001b[1m~/.zshrc\u001b[0m so that it does not perform console I/O\r\n    after the instant prompt preamble. See the link below for details.\r\n\r\n    * You \u001b[1mwill not\u001b[0m see this error message again.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    * Zsh will start \u001b[1mquickly\u001b[0m and prompt will update \u001b[1msmoothly\u001b[0m.\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  - Suppress this warning either by running \u001b[1mp10k configure\u001b[0m or by manually\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    defining the following parameter:\r\n\r\n      \u001b[33mtypeset\u001b[39m -g POWERLEVEL9K_INSTANT_PROMPT=quiet\r\n\r\n    * You \u001b[1mwill not\u001b[0m see this error message again.\r\n    * Zsh will start \u001b[1mquickly\u001b[0m but prompt will \u001b[1mjump down\u001b[0m after initialization.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  - Disable instant prompt either by running \u001b[1mp10k configure\u001b[0m or by manually\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    defining the following parameter:\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "      \u001b[33mtypeset\u001b[39m -g POWERLEVEL9K_INSTANT_PROMPT=off\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    * You \u001b[1mwill not\u001b[0m see this error message again.\r\n    * Zsh will start \u001b[1mslowly\u001b[0m.\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  - Do nothing.\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    * You \u001b[1mwill\u001b[0m see this error message every time you start zsh.\r\n    * Zsh will start \u001b[1mquickly\u001b[0m but prompt will \u001b[1mjump down\u001b[0m after initialization.\r\n\r\nFor details, see:\r\n\u001b]8;;https://github.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k#instant-prompt\u0007https://github.com/romkatv/powerlevel10k#instant-prompt\u001b]8;;\u0007\r\n\r\n\u001b[33m-- console output produced during zsh initialization follows --\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.002, "o", "\u001b[3J\u001b[H\u001b[2J\u001b[3J\u001b[H\u001b[2J\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n                                       \u001b[?25l\u001b[?7l\u001b[0m\u001b[32m\u001b[1m                    'c.\r\n                                                        ,xNMM.\r\n                                                      .OMMMMo\r\n                                                      OMMM0,\r\n                                            .;loddo:' loolloddol;.\r\n                                          cKMMMMMMMMMMNWMMMMMMMMMM0:\r\n                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[33m\u001b[1m .KMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMWd.\r\n                                        XMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMX.\r\n                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[31m\u001b[1m;MMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMM:\r\n                                       :MMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMM:\r\n                                       \u001b[0m\u001b[31m\u001b[1m.MMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMX.\r\n                                        kMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMWd.\r\n                                        \u001b[0m\u001b[35m\u001b[1m.XMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMMk\r\n                                         .XMMM"]
